      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "java script single threaded vayako le garda\n it can't run code and GC parallelly.\nso engine stops your code for a while \nand looks to heap and if there is any object\ndeferenced ir will free heap memory. and code \nagain start to run . so GC interrupts execution\nof code during running.",
      "fontSize": 16,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "java script single threaded vayako le garda\n it can't run code and GC parallelly.\nso engine stops your code for a while \nand looks to heap and if there is any object\ndeferenced ir will free heap memory. and code \nagain start to run . so GC interrupts execution\nof code during running.",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
